The last king of Egypt Ahmed Fuad II lives in exile in Switzerland, but do recent changes in his country make him want his throne back? Also on today's show - Nuzhat and Zaheer Kidvai from Karachi, whose married partnership began at sea in the merchant navy, and continued at home as human rights campaigners, despite the risks involved. Show less